# Bot Framework
Microsoft bot framework v4 is a collection of services, tools, and SDKs that offers developer powerful foundation to create, and connect smart bots to channels. The channel can be simple web chat which integrates with website or app, facebook channel or skype channel.

![image.png](./images/botecosystem.png)

# Pre-requisites
sudo apt-get install libsecret-1-dev

npm install -g npm
npm install -g yo

npm install -g generator-botbuilder


# Create Echo Bot using Scaffolder
yo botbuilder

